{"tid":1757850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"毛孟靜：又要懷疑咁多汽油彈到底喺邊度黎","createTime":"2019-11-26T17:26:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T18:22:56.000Z","uid":171273,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e3ce4f8327978dfbe0c6510fa5e37a120e6399ef","tid":1757850,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T17:26:09.000Z","msg":"Claudia Mo/毛孟靜<br />\n&middot; 2 hrs &middot;<br />\n <br />\n北京之前真係以為香港「民意逆轉」咗<br />\n#建制蛆蟲會贏區選<br />\n就鞏固我一直的想法 #警察攻打中大理大，確係故意喺選舉前引發製造暴力嚟 #嚇香港人（之謂旨暴製亂）<br />\n#<span style=\"color: red;\">又要懷疑咁多汽油彈到底喺邊度黎</span>￼<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n#眾新聞 //帕爾馬（James Palmer）在〈Hong Kongers Break Beijing's Delusions of Victory／港人打破了北京的勝利幻想〉的文章說，他問了中國官媒旗艦英文《中國日報》、《環球時報》英文版、中共機關報《人民日報》的外籍及本地編輯和新聞工作者，這些隱名的人士表示，每一份報章，在11月24日香港區議會選舉之前，假定建制派大勝的稿件已經交給編輯（at each paper, copy was filed to editors the night before the Nov. 24 elections assuming a strong victory for the establishment）。他說他在2009年至2016年擔任《環球時報》編輯七年，「從未見過類似事件要事先寫好稿件」（never saw copy filed ahead of time for similar events）。//"},{"pid":"50058af5b0517a41320ee183f1dc04794566995d","tid":1757850,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T17:27:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"903ded7dd8632a89741685d93405fe5044d37cf2","tid":1757850,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T17:27:29.000Z","msg":"係咪又係曲"},{"pid":"ca65ecfa22c30edb0004e745830f3019de7822bc","tid":1757850,"uid":7948,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T17:29:09.000Z","msg":"唔係曲 前線手足講得好清楚<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ejUGZjhu594\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FejUGZjhu594&d=AiROHBMCWVTnLPrCQVkx92WjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=68356737\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ejUGZjhu594</a>"},{"pid":"ef015a6145a889a55187f656b35d38e735a124ac","tid":1757850,"uid":171273,"like":2,"dislike":0,"scor